        "TileImage": "$($repository 9b2c906e-d66d-4d88-a578-a626e29acf6e).Image",
        "Description": "47, I&apos;ve heard from a few fellow ICA agents that this year for Halloween you are wanting to be Michael Meyers. I&apos;m sorry to disappoint you, but five employees in Miami have also decided to dress up as Michael this year. And I guess it&apos;s not that hard to dress up as someone who has the same name as you. So 47, maybe your persuasiveness will show em who the real Michael is. And it might be a good idea to try and find something that resembles him. Good luck.\r\rSincerley,\rDiana Burnwood",
